						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone standing in front of the temple of Kallēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record states that a hero (name lost), who was the son of <hi rend="bold">Amṛi[ta]-Nāyaka</hi> died in a fight on <hi rend="bold">Thursday, Kārtika śu. 8,</hi> in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Bahudhānya.</hi> The characters belong to the <hi rend="bold">14-15th century A.D.</hi></p>						

